		dark:hover:bg-opacity-10			
		focus:outline-none
		focus-visible:ring-4
		rounded-md
		group
		ring-aurora0
	dark:ring-frost1
		ring-offset-4
	ring-offset-snow2
	dark:ring-offset-night0					
		">
		<svg role="img" class="w-8 h-8 mr-3 transition stroke-transparent fill-aurora0 dark:fill-frost1" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><title>LinkedIn</title><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433c-1.144 0-2.063-.926-2.063-2.065 0-1.138.92-2.063 2.063-2.063 1.14 0 2.064.925 2.064 2.063 0 1.139-.925 2.065-2.064 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
		Juan Martín Jaimes Mendoza
		</a>
		<a target="_blank" href="mailto:jmjaimesmendoza@gmail.com" class="			
		flex
		mr-auto	
		text-center
		text-xl
		px-6
		py-1
		text-aurora0
		dark:text-frost1
		transition
